    "product_details_gLrgBJ": {
      "type": "product-details",
      "blocks": {
        "description_w7TU9P": {
          "type": "description",
          "settings": {
            "description_heading": "Introduction"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_PAyNwP": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Key Features",
            "content": "<ul><li>16 Driver Balanced Armature Architecture</li><li>Gemstone Faceplate Design</li><li>5 Way Passive Crossover</li><li>4 Bass | 4 Mid | 2 Mid-High | 2 High | 4 Super High</li><li>48\" Epsilon Monocrystalline IEM Cable 4.4mm Balanced<br/></li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_n38dzJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The Most Sophisticated Transducer Architecture",
            "content": "<p>The Black Malus employs an advanced 16-driver configuration, including an array of 4 AAW proprietary Vented Miniature Balanced Armature Power Woofers to cover the frequency range. This woofer array delivers substantial bass presence while maintaining a compact footprint. The design incorporates a specially engineered 4 super-high armature driver arrays housed in a 3D-printed manifold, positioned close to the user's eardrum to eliminate sound pressure decay and unwanted resonance typical in tubed designs. </p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_fPHfQE": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "“Sandwich” Hybrid Enclosure Design",
            "content": "<p>Black Malus’ construction is a testament to the harmony of cutting-edge technology and artisanal craftsmanship, brought together in a sophisticated “sandwich” hybrid enclosure design. At its foundation is a precision-engineered 3D-printed acoustic chamber, enabling complex internal geometries that optimize airflow and resonance control for uncompromising sound performance. This is seamlessly integrated with a CNC-machined stainless steel mid-case, selected not only for its modern aesthetic but also for its structural rigidity—particularly around the reinforced 2-pin connector stock, ensuring long-term durability and a secure cable interface. Capping this layered design is a handcrafted resin-based faceplate, each one individually poured and polished to reveal mesmerizing swirls and vibrant color gradients. This multi-material approach results in a shell that is both acoustically superior and visually captivating, reflecting the same precision and beauty found in Black Malus’ sound signature. </p><p><strong>NOT Available on Custom Fit Version</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_HffCBq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Exclusive Gemstone Faceplate Design",
            "content": "<p>Experience the perfect fusion of artistry and sound with our Opal Infused Faceplate Design. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, each faceplate is a masterpiece, showcasing genuine opal gemstones that shimmer with captivating hues of blues, greens, and fiery reds, creating a design as unique as your music taste. Beyond their stunning aesthetics, these IEMs deliver unparalleled audio clarity, enveloping you in every note, beat, and nuance. Whether you're a musician, audiophile, or style enthusiast, our opal-accented IEMs redefine luxury and performance, turning your listening experience into a visual and auditory marvel.</p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_XefaKL": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Accessories and Warranty",
            "content": "<ul><li>Null Audio Epsilon Monocrystalline IEM Cable</li><li>AAW Carrying Case</li><li>Cleaning Cloth</li><li>LiquidMorph Universal Ear Tips</li><li>Assorted Foam & Silicone Ear Tips</li><li>2 Year Limited Warranty</li></ul>"
          }
        },
